          <h3 class="pageSep"><img class="homeImg" src="https://ssir.org/images/blog/iStockmachinelearning592x333.jpg"
            alt="image of community service"> Hello, fellow changemaker! We are a mission-driven organization building a pathway towards equality,
            entrepreneurship, and a lifetime of self-learning within the U.S. education system. Join a dedicated community of over 1,000 professional
            educators nationwide who strive to build a foundation of knowledge in their students. We recently were honored to be named the 2020 Finalist
            and Winner of the Investing in Innovation federal grant. </h3>
